自己原来是一个良心未泯的人。他一边流泪一边对自己说：你看我仍然是个好人啊，我的内心仍然是有感情的，有人曾经说过我内心冷漠或者缺乏人性，那统统都是鬼话。 第二行眼泪使得这个人更加昂首挺胸起来：他原来不仅是孤立无援的一个人，当他汹涌的泪水与别人流在一处时，他体验到了自己是人类成员的那种感觉，他加入了众人的行列并且感到被接纳，他不仅重新找回了安全感，而且感到自己的生命正在闪闪发光，正在走向光明和出路。"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "95 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/27039705"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I75yu0oWN1I1eEAMaBzI5OTg3OTMg5NCppAUwhAE4mtkCQBtyCDI3MDM5NzA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1621681368.4481525", "card_id": "Q_24123447", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 211}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何判断个人的悟性高低？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "有时候会说一个人，悟性高，悟性是否等于天赋？一个人的理解力，反应速度快是否为悟性的判断标准？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-84814ea97508d33f2ff7c6c2a1291974_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "93 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/24123447"}}, "attached_info": "Cj0I75yu0oWN1I1eEAMaBzE4MzExOTUglb7lnAUwBjiROEAccggyNDEyMzQ0N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "29_1621681368.4485896", "card_id": "Q_267668022", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 142}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "win10 用什么压缩软件好？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如题，大数字压缩有时候会误删，winrar 广告窗口……"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-0857b0859196834d2798dc59549378a6_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "88 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/267668022"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I75yu0oWN1I1eEAMaCDIxNTAwMjE1IPLaxdQFMAs44gRAHXIJMjY3NjY4MDIyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1621681368.4490387", "card_id": "Q_456786411", "feed_specific": {"answe